#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Settings Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू</phrase> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1246 menus.docbook:2007
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Settings Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू</para> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you are looking for is missing, please see <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> in "
"&kde; Fundamentals. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् अन्विष्यमाणः मेनू-वस्तु लुप्तः अस्ति तर्हि कृपया &kde; मौलिकता। अत्र सूचीकृतानि "
"वस्तूनि &kmail; विशिष्टः।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Quick Search bar</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>त्वरित अन्वेषणपट्टिकां दर्शयतु</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables the Quick Search bar, which lets you quickly search for messages "
"matching your criteria."
msgstr ""
"द्रुत-अन्वेषण-पट्टिकां सक्षमं करोति, यत् भवतः मापदण्डेन सह सङ्गत-सन्देशान् शीघ्रं अन्वेष्टुं "
"शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Filters...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>फ़िल्टर्स् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <link linkend=\"filters\">Message Filters</link> dialog."
msgstr "उद्घाटयति<link linkend=\"filters\"> सन्देश-छिद्रकाः</link> संवादः ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Sieve Scripts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>चलनीस्क्रिप्ट् प्रबन्धयन्तु...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your mail server supports sieves (server side filtering), you may "
"configure those scripts here."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतः मेलसर्वरः sieves (server side filtering) समर्थयति तर्हि भवान् ताः स्क्रिप्ट् "
"अत्र विन्यस्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Add Account...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guisubmenu>लेखं योजयतु...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the Account Wizard dialog, which assists in setting up new or "
"additional accounts. Please see <link linkend=\"account-wizard\">Account "
"Wizard</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Account Wizard संवादं आरभते, यत् नूतनानां अतिरिक्तानां वा खातानां स्थापनायां सहायकं भवति "
"। कृपया पश्यन्तु<link linkend=\"account-wizard\"> खाता विजार्ड</link> विस्तरेण कृते।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Automatic Archiving...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>स्वचालितं संग्रहणं विन्यस्यताम्...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Initiates a dialog to set up automatic archiving. See <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Automatic Archiving</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"स्वचालितसंग्रहस्थापनार्थं संवादं आरभते । विस्तरेण <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_archivemail_agent\">स्वचालितसंग्रह</ulink> इति पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kmail;...</guimenuitem> विन्यस्यताम्"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"configure\">Configure &kmail;</link> dialog. There "
"are hundreds of variables to play with. Have fun!"
msgstr ""
"उद्घाटयति<link linkend=\"configure\"> विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु &amp;kmail;</link> संवादः । "
"क्रीडितुं शतशः चराः सन्ति । अश्!"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1323 menus.docbook:2036
#, no-c-format
